<%= title %>:

入款(<%= depositTimes %>笔):
<% deposits.forEach((item, index) => { %>
  <%= new Date(item.createdAt).toLocaleString('zh-CN', { hour12: false }) %>：第<%= index + 1 %>笔：<%= item.amount %>
<% }) %>
共 <%= deposits.reduce((sum, item) => sum + item.amount, 0) %>

下发（<%= widthdrawTimes %>笔）:
<% widthdraws.forEach((item, index) => { %>
  <%= new Date(item.createdAt).toLocaleString('zh-CN', { hour12: false }) %>：第<%= index + 1 %>笔：<%= item.amount %>
<% }) %>
共 <%= widthdraws.reduce((sum, item) => sum + item.amount, 0) %>

费率：<%= (feeRate * 100).toFixed(2) %>%
汇率：<%= exchangeRate %>
